Class GroupByContentPhase

All Implemented Interfaces:
QueueProcessor, Runnable, Future<Void>, RunnableFuture<Void>, javafx.concurrent.Worker<Void>, javafx.event.EventTarget
public class GroupByContentPhase extends Phase
A Phase designed to group files by content. The input is a sequence of collections of pathnames to be grouped. The output is a sequence of collections of pathnames of files with matching contents. Outputs an empty group as an end of file mark.
